[[!meta title="pepper 0.2.2 released"]]

Version 0.2.2 of pepper is now available. This release greatly improves
the performance of the Git backend and adds two built-in report
scripts. One of them, the participation report, is on display at the
[[Gallery]].

A more detailed listing of the changes can be found in the [change
log](ChangeLog). As usual, source tarballs can be found at the
[[Download]] section.
